long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
You are fed to open tabs one by one when you need to always open the same ... And you dream to be able to group them by themes or needs and open them in 1 click! I think that Quick Launch'em is the application you need!

Thank you to note my app and make comments, I'll be happy to give you more!

Download, enjoy and share ;) Thank you
